00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:02.000
So calls align and tab options.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:07.000
So columns are automatically aligned in gray tables.

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:11.000
If you just take, like, exible, things will be aligned in certain ways.

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:13.000
